Table And Fields by macros
Things needed for review results for one task
\

#- {defaultplugin="textfield" .fieldCell}
%% 'XX_Riitauta=Riitauta: Kirjoita t채h채n, jos et tykk채채 arvioista' | gfields('cols: 25') -%%
\

#- {area="XX_fields" visible="%% False | isview%%" nocache="true" collapse="true"}
Arviointitilanne XX

#- {defaultplugin="numericfield" readonly="view" .fieldCell}
%%REVIEW_FIELDS("XX", arvosteltavia)%%

#- {area_end="XX_fields"}
\

``` {#XX_demotable plugin="tableForm" visible="%% False | isview%%" nocache="true"}
%%REVIEW_TABLE("XX",arvosteltavia)%%
```

``` {#reviewUpdateRunner_XX plugin="jsrunner"}
%%REVIEW_UPDATE("XX",arvosteltavia,1,6)%%
```
